stories.text:
I am looking for a service where I can send (text ideally) a picture of a page out of my physical notebook and a human will organize and transcribe the notes for me digitally. When I search for something like this all I can find is OCR tech or digital note taking solutions. I don't want to use upwork etc. because of the variability in the load. One week I may need 10 pages next I may only need 1.

I know this is an old school problem but I have tried digital note taking and it just doesn't work for me.
